# Math Learning System Rules

## Initial Path
### Basics
- Users start with basic math fundamentals as the recommended path
- A basic module turns green when:
  - User has correctly solved at least 4 exercises
  - User maintains at least 75% accuracy
- Completing all basic math modules unlocks:
  - "Välgrundad" achievement
  - Access to calibration phase

### Premium vs Non-Premium
- Non-premium users:
  - Access "Oändligt" mode instead of calibration
  - Randomly generated questions
  
### Calibration Phase
- Structure:
  - 4 questions from each formula sheet module
  - Module status indicators:
    - Yellow: At least 3 correct answers
    - Green: Same as yellow plus average time per correct answer under 30 seconds
- Completion unlocks:
  - "Kalibrerad och klar" achievement
  - Access to Grind formula sheet

## Grind Phase
### Category Classification
- Yellow Status Requirements:
  - Minimum 75% correct answers from last 10 questions
- Green Status Requirements:
  - Same as yellow
  - Maximum 30 seconds per correct answer

### Progression
1. System generates questions from red categories until none remain
   - Unlocks "Välformulerad" milestone
2. System generates questions from yellow categories until only green remain
   - Unlocks "Formel-1 bladet" milestone

## Grind Tests
### Test Options

| Test Type | Duration (min) | Questions |
|-----------|---------------|-----------|
| XYZ       | 12           | 12        |
| NOG       | 10           | 6         |
| KVA       | 10           | 10        |
| DTK       | 23           | 12        |
| Full      | 55           | 40        |

### Additional Activities
- "Andra chansen": Retry test with previously failed questions

